<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Complete Your XSpaceGrow Order</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
    .cta-button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3); }
    .order-summary { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .suggestions { background-color: #e8f4f8; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .device-highlight { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7 0%, #fab1a0 100%); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .urgency-badge { background-color: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 15px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>💳 Complete Your XSpaceGrow Order</h1>
      <p>Your IoT devices are waiting for you!</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name || @user.email.split('@').first.titleize %>,</p>

      <p>We noticed there was an issue processing payment for your XSpaceGrow order. Don't worry - your order is still reserved, and we're here to help you complete it!</p>

      <!-- Order Summary -->
      <div class="order-summary">
        <h3>📦 Order #<%= @order.id %></h3>
        <% if @device_count > 0 %>
          <div class="device-highlight">
            <strong>🚀 <%= @device_count %> IoT Device<%= @device_count > 1 ? 's' : '' %> Ready for Activation</strong>
            <p>Start monitoring your environment data in minutes!</p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        
        <% @order_items.each do |item| %>
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
            <span><%= item.product.name %> × <%= item.quantity %></span>
            <span><strong>$<%= item.total %></strong></span>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 15px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; border-top: 2px solid #667eea;">
          <span>Total:</span>
          <span>$<%= @total %></span>
        </div>

        <% if @hours_since_failure %>
          <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
            <span class="urgency-badge">⏰ <%= @hours_since_failure %> hours ago</span>
            Payment attempt failed
          </p>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <!-- Retry CTA -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= @retry_url %>" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">
          🔄 Complete Payment Now
        </a>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;">
          Your order is reserved for <strong>48 hours</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Helpful Suggestions -->
      <% if @suggestions.present? %>
        <div class="suggestions">
          <h4>💡 Quick Solutions:</h4>
          <ul>
            <% @suggestions.each do |suggestion| %>
              <li><%= suggestion %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <!-- Why Complete Your Order -->
      <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <h3>🌟 Why Complete Your Order?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Real-time Monitoring:</strong> Start tracking temperature, humidity, and more instantly</li>
          <li><strong>Smart Alerts:</strong> Get notified when conditions change</li>
          <li><strong>Historical Data:</strong> Build valuable trend analysis</li>
          <li><strong>Easy Setup:</strong> Device activation takes less than 5 minutes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Support -->
      <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 30px;">
        <h4>Need Help? 🤝</h4>
        <p>Our support team is ready to assist:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:support@xspacegrow.com">support@xspacegrow.com</a></li>
          <li>💬 Live Chat: Available on our website</li>
          <li>📞 Phone: 1-800-XSPACE-1</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        Thanks for choosing XSpaceGrow!<br>
        <strong>The XSpaceGrow Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        XSpaceGrow • IoT Device Management Platform<br>
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>">Visit Dashboard</a> • 
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/support">Support Center</a>
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px;">
        This email was sent regarding your order #<%= @order.id %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>